column5: Hello all, I didn't want to post anything formal. However I did want to say that I am very impressed with this community and the members that it is comprised of. I am part of several Ontario online fishing communities and I must say that the amount of quality discussion and sheer quantity of discussion you have here is unmatched. Have been looking in from the outside for sometime now and finally decided to join. Hopefullyy, you will all have me.  Phil  oh yea...catch me if you can
Hey Phil !!! Welcome to the familly Buddy !!! You are right, this place is a home away from home, with some of the coolest people i have ever met
Welcome to OFC Phil Looking forward to reading your kayak adventures Leechman
Welcome aboard Phil, you will definately enjoy yourself here.  We have a few kayak fisherman aboard here already  Joey
Hmmmm I'm gonna guess that you maybe chase musky in that kayak?  Welcome from R.C.
